Thomas+N.+Garavan&amp;rft.au=Pat+Costine&amp;rft.au=Noreen+Heraty&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ATraining+and+development\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-6\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation book\">Derek Torrington; Laura Hall &amp; Stephen Taylor (2004). <i>Human Resource Management</i>. Pearson Education. p.&#160;363. <a href=\"/wiki/International_Standard_Book_Number\" title=\"International Standard Book Number\">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href=\"/wiki/Special:BookSources/9780273687139\" title=\"Special:BookSources/9780273687139\">9780273687139</a>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Human+Resource+Management&amp;rft.pages=363&amp;rft.pub=Pearson+Education&amp;rft.date=2004&amp;rft.isbn=9780273687139&amp;rft.au=Derek+Torrington&amp;rft.au=Laura+Hall&amp;rft.au=Stephen+Taylor&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ATraining+and+development\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-7\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-7\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">John Hoover, PhD <i>\"How to Work for an Idiot: Survive and Thrive Without Killing Your Boss\"</i> (Career Press <a href=\"/wiki/International_Standard_Book_Number\" title=\"International Standard Book Number\">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href=\"/wiki/Special:BookSources/1564147045\" title=\"Special:BookSources/1564147045\">1564147045</a>/<a href=\"/wiki/International_Standard_Book_Number\" title=\"International Standard Book Number\">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href=\"/wiki/Special:BookSources/978-1564147042\" title=\"Special:BookSources/978-1564147042\">978-1564147042</a>)</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-8\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-8\">^</a></b